{"tid":61561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港極端天氣破近30項紀錄 天文台長籲勿追風睇結霜","createTime":"2016-12-31T10:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T15:45:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8e96db0cb47cc6367bde942816845780af745f","tid":61561,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161231/large/1483149397_e742.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161231%2Flarge%2F1483149397_e742.jpg&h=87822f4b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今年6月本港錄得連續4日35&deg;C或以上高溫。(資料圖片) <br />\n<br />\n天文台長岑智明在電台節目表示，本港極端天氣日益頻繁出現，過去2年打破近30個天文台開台以來的紀錄，例如今年6月錄得連續4日35&deg;C或以上高溫。他認為氣候暖化的極端情況，是人類工業革命以來不斷排放溫室氣體的「共業」。 <br />\n<br />\n岑智明指，難以評估明年本港會否出現極端天氣，而市民也未必了解如何應付罕見天氣情況，呼籲市民避免在颱風或結霜時追風追雪。他指天文台正研究提供兩星期或更長時間的天氣預報，並會加強澄清坊間對網上數據的誤解。 <br />\n他亦憂慮美國候任總統特朗普上台後，執行巴黎氣候協議的情況有變，強調如全球碳排放水平不變，本港氣溫到世紀末將會上升攝氏3至6度。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161231/56113797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161231%2F56113797&d=c8hjhPu9Z%2FxIFSGlYmaht5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=093c0982\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161231%2F56113797&h=cd4d1885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161231/56113797</a>"},{"pid":"b23cf7f2b8068a745954efac2d0ec9893c46dd4e","tid":61561,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"我頭先落街都係短衫褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859fc26fd43148c35d1e1addeaf204d7b20d6042","tid":61561,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:40:41.000Z","msg":"今日幾熱"},{"pid":"0821f76b5e08eab4b4db463643cfc3a827ba0369","tid":61561,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike